title: Barrett-Jackson REVVED UP
overview: Barrett-Jackson REVVED UP is bringing the best rides and biggest highlights from the world's greatest collector car auction: Barrett-Jackson. Strap in, hit the gas and come along for the ride as the best of the best go under the hammer in a high stakes, no reserve auction where every car sells. Each year, thousands of the world's most sought-after, unique and valuable automobiles cross the Barrett-Jackson auction block. We're heading to the bright lights of Las Vegas where over 670 vehicles were sold for a total of $33.3 million dollars.Â
